I"›<h2 id="how-to-setup-samba-as-a-file-server-using-ubuntu">How to setup Samba as a file server using Ubuntu</h2>
<p>You may be wondering what is Samba? Well, Samba is a software package that provides stable and fast file, folder, and printer sharing between Windows and Linux computers. It can also act as a domain controller just like Active Directory which handles the authentication requests on a domain.</p>
